A strategy and policy needs to developed to bring in the leadership of these religious groups into the national plan

They need to understand the National goal of reducing Rzero and to drastically modify their social contact behavior with the community outside of their religion

Modelling / simulation needs to be done to understand their role in an outbreak and how they can play a role during the second wave

This needs to be viewed in the context of herd immunity
